<div class="thumbinner" style="width:227px;"><a href="/wiki/File:King_Alcohol_and_his_Prime_Minister.jpg" class="image" title="&quot;King Alcohol and his Prime Minister&quot; circa 1820"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a3/King_Alcohol_and_his_Prime_Minister.jpg/225px-King_Alcohol_and_his_Prime_Minister.jpg" width="225" height="509" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
